===Etymology===
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*liŋ||neck}} (STEDT under PTB *g/m-liŋ, {{zh-ref|Schuessler 2007}}). Cognate with {{cog|bo|མཇིང་པ||neck}}, {{cog|lus|ring||neck}}, {{cog|my|လည်||neck}}. Semantics: "neck, collar" > ("to take by the neck" > ) "to lead, to guide" ({{zh-ref|Schuessler 2007}}).

